<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_OSIK" id="금전적-기대값-분석">금전적 기대값 분석<a href="https://gracefullight.dev/en/pe/pm/risk-analysis/#%EA%B8%88%EC%A0%84%EC%A0%81-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8C%80%EA%B0%92-%EB%B6%84%EC%84%9D" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to heading" title="Direct link to heading">​</a></h3>
